  "body": "<p>Loved using this months kits from Studio Calico, <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/planetarium?aff=6cc2c70f\">Planetarium</a>. Here's how this layout came together using the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/planetarium-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">main kit only</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"1a-DSC_1165-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599894187549-98HOQEPWW5P3P5R9BHB1/1a-DSC_1165-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"1b-DSC_1166-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599894214358-5P6UT1KMKF4C408XIVTW/1b-DSC_1166-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1c-DSC_1167-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599894187935-BLY2SST2YFLI0F6C1EUU/1c-DSC_1167-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1d-DSC_1168-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599894189405-VVOBZ0LE1SJMLVAY6J5C/1d-DSC_1168-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1e-DSC_1169-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599894189830-VUTIA72YQBERZZKM0SS2/1e-DSC_1169-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1f-DSC_1170-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599894190409-YBID0TS2M1CB3SDGKKIX/1f-DSC_1170-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1g-amy_sc_may_1-600x438.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599894190858-LIN2X4QHASSL3V8842W9/1g-amy_sc_may_1-600x438.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1g-amy_sc_may-560x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599894191444-WE0ZDRFWGROT53C4GCP0/1g-amy_sc_may-560x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I made quite a few layouts using these awesome kits, which you can view in <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/creative-team-gallery/planetarium/scrapbook/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">the gallery</a>. Ironically I am also headed from Perth to Melbourne tomorrow. Can't wait to see some of you at <a href=\"http://www.bhglive.com.au/melbourne/\">Better Homes &amp; Gardens LIVE</a>!</p>"
